---
title: Warm Kumara, Basil Haloumi & Rocket Salad with Herbed Hazelnut Picada
description: If you like pesto, you’ll love picada. Think of it as the rustic Spanish cousin of our other favourite sauce. Rich and nutty and so easy to throw together, you’ll love the way it takes this dish to the next level.
